The kitchen offers S/S appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry. The master suite offers a serene retreat, complete w/an ensuite bath for added privacy and comfort. Two additional bedrooms & main floor laundry provide versatility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. Venture downstairs you will find a fully finished basement suite w/it's own laundry. Step outside to the expansive backyard oasis, where you'll find a sprawling patio, deck, and fire pit area, ideal for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying the outdoors in style. The large yard offers ample room for gardening, play, or pets to roam freely. Located close to Manning Dr, Shopping and more. ALL THIS HOME NEEDS IS YOU! (31128454)

Welcome to the beautiful and highly desirable community of Highlands, where this 1 & a half storey home has been standing tall since 1918. With 2 bedrooms and a den on the main floor and 2 bedrooms upstairs or 1 massive bedroom with a nursery or office (the options are endless) this home is awaiting a new family to come and call it home. And bring it back to its original glory! The basement is fully finished with a large rec room and 3 piece washroom. Once you're in the backyard you'll feel like you're in your own personal oasis. There's also a large shed with a gravel pathway that leads to the front street and a large double detached garage facing the back alley. The home backs onto a playground, perfect for your kids to play in and not have to worry about a long walk. Close to a bunch of restaurants and amenities. The lot is 66 ft by 130 ft (20.1m x 39.6) ideal for redevelopment or restoration. The property is being sold as-is, where-is with no warrants or representations. (31139736)

Results.PublicRemarks: Stately Westmount gem seamlessly blends its historical appeal with modernized upgrades! This elegant 1,985 sq ft family home rests on a serene, tree-lined street amid similar legacy residences. Over time a labour of love updated many important features of the home: The basement was lowered, extended, separate entrance added and new floor poured in the 1990's. At the same time the kitchen was renovated and an addition at the rear added a bathroom, family room & 2 upstairs back bedrooms with their own balcony. Front bedrooms were reinsulated, redrywalled in 2000. Main bath renovated in 2004. A new, oversized, insulated double garage was built in 2018. The covered front porch was lifted & stabilized & the front living room re-drywalled, insulated and painted in 2023.  Furnace was replaced in the last couple of years also. Stairs to attic were installed so that the attic space could be developed. This captivating character home is steps to vibrant 124 St, all amenities, transportation & minutes from downtown! (31217852)

Wonderful location in sought after Parkview. This great 4-level split has approximately 1800 sq ft of living space plus a basement. South facing back yard, walking distance to schools and downtown transportation. Good sized kitchen with lovely oak cabinets and a dining area leading out to large deck. Three bedrooms on upper level and a walkout to a three season sunroom from the lower level through French doors. There is also a large family room with a gas fireplace to keep you warm in the winter months. Comes with newer windows and roof and an oversized 24' x 26' garage for extra storage. This is a perfect home to make your own. (31274802)

Steps to RAVINE! Strathcona custom build over 1460 sq ft half duplex offers 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath with double detached garage.* There is a three-inch noise-deadening space between the other unit for quietness; the 2 x 6 walls are cross-braced. Foam insulation was blown into the exterior walls before the plywood was applied.* There are engineered trusses in the basement and no common wall between the two halves--rather there is a 3 inch dead space for almost complete noise suppression.* A bright home with triple-pane windows and spacious-sized rooms. Built-in wood shelving and the functional alcove.* The master bedroom has a 4 piece en-suite and a walk-in closet. The other two bedrooms are good size.* The basement is finished and features another bedroom, family room, a full bath, a high-efficiency furnace, and B.I. Vacuum System. * Miles of walking trails. A rare find! (31232344)
